WEBVTT

00:00.045 --> 00:02.172
<i>Previously on Better Call Saul...</i>

00:02.540 --> 00:06.396
- Tommy, about the electricity.
- I know how it sounds but it's real.

00:06.689 --> 00:09.461
I'm picking up that driver.
And if he knows you, that's bad.

00:09.516 --> 00:11.221
The cops keeping it out of the papers.

00:11.448 --> 00:13.592
He wanted to put the cops onto Hector.

00:13.595 --> 00:16.385
- He forgot all about you.
- I haven't forgotten him.

00:16.455 --> 00:19.095
1216 Rosella Drive, Scottsdale, Arizona.

00:19.295 --> 00:20.427
This was no mistake.

00:20.433 --> 00:21.619
He sabotaged me.

00:21.732 --> 00:24.290
Remember me? The answer is no.

00:24.466 --> 00:27.284
I know he was here. I know what he did.

